'''Kiyovu Sports Association''', rizwi cyane ku izina rya '''SC Kiyovu Sports''', '''Kiyovu Sports''' cyangwa '''Kiyovu''', ni club [[Umupira w’amaguru|y'umupira w'amaguru]] iherereye i [[Kigali]], mu [[Rwanda]] . Kuri ubu iyi kipe irushanwa mu gikombe [[Shampiyona y’ icyiciro cya mbere mu mupira w’amaguru mu Rwanda|cy’umupira wamaguru mu Rwanda]], ikina imikino yayo murugo kuri Stade Mumena cyangwa [[Stade Amahoro|kuri Sitade Amahoro]] . Ikipe yabigenewe muri iki gihe irushanwa mu cyiciro cya gatatu cyu Rwanda . <ref>[http://progressrwanda.rw/2014/03/tricky-test-for-police-against-sc-kiyovu/ Tricky test for Police against SC Kiyovu]</ref> Iyi kipe yatwaye ibikombe birindwi bya shampiyona, ibikombe bitatu, ndetse nigikombe kimwe, kandi niyo kipe yonyine yo mu Rwanda yagiye muri shampiyona yose idatsinzwe mu 1990.

Kiyovu Sport Club niyo kipe yambere yumupira wamaguru yu Rwanda yinjiye muri Shampiyona yumupira wamaguru, hagati ya 1948 na 1957. Batangiriye mu cyiciro cya mbere bamanurwa rimwe gusa, muri 2017.

